# India AI Tracker Hub - Project Overview

## Project Purpose
This is an **India AI Tracker Hub** - a comprehensive platform tracking India's AI revolution. The project showcases:
- 20+ Large Language Models (LLMs)
- 8+ Text-to-Speech (TTS) models
- 2+ Image generation models
- 2+ Video generation models
- 20+ organizations
- Timeline coverage from 2020-2025

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: Vite
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + CSS animations
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui (Radix UI primitives)
- **State Management**: React Query (@tanstack/react-query)
- **Routing**: React Router DOM
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Charts**: Recharts
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Zod validation
- **Themes**: next-themes for dark/light mode
- **Notifications**: Sonner + shadcn/ui toasts

## Project Structure
- **Entry Point**: [main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx) renders the App component
- **Main App**: [App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx) sets up routing, providers, and global components
- **Pages**: [src/pages/](mdc:src/pages) contains route components
  - [Index.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Index.tsx) - Main dashboard with tabs for Timeline, Organizations, and Progress
  - [NotFound.tsx](mdc:src/pages/NotFound.tsx) - 404 page
- **Components**: [src/components/](mdc:src/components) contains custom components
  - [InteractiveTimeline.tsx](mdc:src/components/InteractiveTimeline.tsx) - Timeline visualization
  - [CompanyProfiles.tsx](mdc:src/components/CompanyProfiles.tsx) - Organization profiles display
  - [ProgressDashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/ProgressDashboard.tsx) - Analytics and progress metrics
- **UI Components**: [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui) contains shadcn/ui components
- **Utilities**: [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts) contains utility functions (cn for className merging)
- **Hooks**: [src/hooks/](mdc:src/hooks) contains custom React hooks
- **Styles**: [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) contains global styles and Tailwind imports

## Development Setup
- Package manager: npm (with optional Bun support)
- Dev server: `npm run dev`
- Build: `npm run build`
- Linting: `npm run lint` (ESLint with React hooks plugin)
- TypeScript configuration in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) and [tsconfig.app.json](mdc:tsconfig.app.json)

